Of course that's not possible!

13
00:00:48,300 --> 00:00:49,300
That wasn't for me.

14
00:00:49,367 --> 00:00:52,700
Where would we sell this second line?

15
00:00:52,767 --> 00:00:54,367
Right here.

16
00:00:54,433 --> 00:00:56,100
In this shop.

17
00:00:56,167 --> 00:00:59,233
