18
00:00:59,300 --> 00:01:00,633
You just want to get revenge!

19
00:01:00,700 --> 00:01:02,967
And what's wrong with that?

20
00:01:03,033 --> 00:01:05,200
That's not beautiful!

21
00:01:05,267 --> 00:01:08,533
Here we go again,
"It's not beautiful."

22
