You just say that to shut me up.

23
00:01:13,400 --> 00:01:14,933
You are so--

24
00:01:15,000 --> 00:01:16,867
Please, cut it out!

25
00:01:16,933 --> 00:01:19,300
We're expecting a customer.

26
00:01:20,433 --> 00:01:22,900
It's like watching a parent and child
bickering.

27
00:01:22,967 --> 00:01:25,200
I don't recall having a child like this!

28
00:01:25,267 --> 00:01:27,133
And I don't recall ever being your child!

29
