We're so glad to see you here again.

30
00:01:36,500 --> 00:01:41,700
It's such a shame that
the trunk show was canceled.

31
00:01:42,600 --> 00:01:44,233
Indeed.

32
00:01:44,300 --> 00:01:48,400
