Yes.

34
00:01:51,633 --> 00:01:53,200
Everything was ready to go.

35
00:01:53,700 --> 00:01:55,500
The new line?

36
00:01:55,567 --> 00:01:59,633
I wish I could have seen it.
I was so looking forward to it.

37
00:02:00,500 --> 00:02:01,733
Do you have it here now?

38
00:02:02,300 --> 00:02:03,300
Yes.

39
00:02:03,800 --> 00:02:05,400
Well...

40
00:02:05,467 --> 00:02:07,567
Will you let me see it?

41
00:02:19,567 --> 00:02:21,900
Come this way.

42
00:02:21,967 --> 00:02:23,000
Excuse me.

43
00:02:26,867 --> 00:02:28,100
Wow.

44
00:02:28,167 --> 00:02:29,200
It's beautiful.

45
00:02:29,267 --> 00:02:30,900
Thank you.

46
00:02:33,567 --> 00:02:39,400
I'm honored to be able to see
President Nanjo's work up close.

47
00:02:40,500 --> 00:02:42,033
This nightie

48
00:02:43,267 --> 00:02:45,267
is really beautiful.

49
00:02:53,667 --> 00:02:55,333
I wish we could have shown it...

50
00:02:58,600 --> 00:03:01,000
more properly at the trunk show.

51
00:03:03,667 --> 00:03:05,300
Especially to customers like you,

52
