I'm very sorry.

54
00:03:18,100 --> 00:03:19,100
No.

55
00:03:28,433 --> 00:03:29,500
THE LUXURY OF CHOOSING
STORY LINGERIE

56
00:03:29,567 --> 00:03:30,633
POPULAR LINGERIE BRAND
STORY

57
00:03:30,700 --> 00:03:31,933
FEATURE WRITTEN BY
SHUKO OYAMA

58
00:03:33,767 --> 00:03:35,200
You're like a child,

59
00:03:36,500 --> 00:03:39,733
getting upset when
things don't go her way.

60
00:03:41,633 --> 00:03:44,433
You want them to admit they're wrong.

61
00:03:45,633 --> 00:03:47,600
You have a strong ego.

62
00:03:48,467 --> 00:03:49,900
You said it yourself, boss...

63
00:03:52,367 --> 00:03:54,500
that maybe you were the presumptuous one.

64
00:03:54,567 --> 00:03:55,733
That's right.

65
00:03:56,900 --> 00:03:58,567
All I'm doing

66
00:03:58,633 --> 00:04:01,800
is giving the business of mass production
the respect it deserves.

67
00:04:02,700 --> 00:04:07,167
That doesn't mean Emotion is ready to
take on that kind business.

68
00:04:07,233 --> 00:04:09,733
So then, nothing will change.

69
00:04:14,533 --> 00:04:16,833
Is being consistent such a bad thing?

70
00:04:18,300 --> 00:04:21,967
By remembering how I felt 30 years ago,

71
00:04:22,033 --> 00:04:24,567
I was able to go back to my roots.

72
00:04:25,500 --> 00:04:26,700
But this!

73
00:04:27,700 --> 00:04:29,933
You want us to just stand back and watch?

74
00:04:34,667 --> 00:04:37,633
We can't just instantly start
a second line.

75
00:04:39,333 --> 00:04:41,800
We have no money or personnel.

76
00:04:43,167 --> 00:04:44,367
You must face the facts.

77
00:04:48,400 --> 00:04:49,500
I know.

78
00:04:52,267 --> 00:04:57,067
And yet, if you were to suppress
your annoyingly persistent feelings,

79
00:04:57,133 --> 00:04:59,100
that would really be

80
00:05:00,267 --> 00:05:01,267
a shame!

81
00:05:05,967 --> 00:05:07,433
Don't focus on revenge.

82
00:05:09,367 --> 00:05:13,567
Pour all that passion into
something you can do right now.

83
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:20,800
I...

84
00:05:25,500 --> 00:05:27,100
want everyone to know.

85
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:31,867
This shop sells
the most beautiful lingerie

86
00:05:31,933 --> 00:05:33,333
in the entire world.

87
00:05:35,200 --> 00:05:37,367
No matter how beautiful the product is,

88
00:05:37,433 --> 00:05:39,533
if no one knows about it,
it's as if it didn't exist.

89
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:42,767
So...

90
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:45,167
In these.

91
00:05:46,333 --> 00:05:47,800
In all of these!

92
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:51,700
I'll have them run an article
about Emotion.

93
