113
00:07:00,100 --> 00:07:01,767
I know that!

114
00:07:01,833 --> 00:07:03,533
Do you remember where we first met?

115
00:07:04,400 --> 00:07:06,933
Yeah, you were working in a textile shop.

116
00:07:08,367 --> 00:07:11,300
