kept coming by!

237
00:13:10,100 --> 00:13:11,833
And they'd leave their products.

238
00:13:11,900 --> 00:13:15,767
Having models use the products
is the quickest way to sell.

239
00:13:15,833 --> 00:13:17,633
It doesn't cost any money.

240
00:13:17,700 --> 00:13:18,700
Money?

241
00:13:19,667 --> 00:13:23,567
